Cookies set by third parties
Reed.co.uk works with a number of third parties to provide services which help us to keep the website tailored to our users' needs. Some of these partners use cookies to help them deliver these services. A list of third party cookies can be found below:
Cookie name
Purpose
TinyMCE
Allows text to be pasted into the covering letter on job applications
